
New tabbed view application
-----------------------------


* Remove the "SecondViewController" .m .h from the project (to trash)

* Drag in the SDK folder (Copy items to destination groups folder = YES)
  * Create groups for added folders

* In each of the story board files,
   change the "Custom Class" property of the controller object from "SecondViewController" to "StageVideo" (SDK name)

* Select the project in the folder view, then "Build Phases"

  In the "Link with binaries" section, hit it "+" and add the frameworks
   +  AVFoundation
   +  OpenAl
   +  MediaPlayer


* Select Build Settings
   *  Apple LLVM 5.0 - language c++
      > C++ standard library - set to libstdc++ (GNU C++ standard library)

